WEBVTT

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:31.376
neighbor against neighbor.

00:03:31.400 --> 00:03:34.256
And at the age of 12 I experienced war,

00:03:34.280 --> 00:03:35.880
destitution in my family,

00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:39.960
the deaths of 22
of my relatives in horrible ways,

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:43.760
as well as the murder of my elder brother.

00:03:47.040 --> 00:03:48.800
I witnessed killing ...

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:53.816
animals feeding on corpses in the streets,

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:55.576
starvation all around me,

00:03:55.600 --> 00:03:57.736
wanton, horrific violence --

00:03:57.760 --> 00:03:58.960
senseless violence.